<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (qạl ly ạlsẖyṭạn kẖṭạyạk .. kẖlt yswʿ ynsạk)2
 (lkny bnfsy smʿth .. byqwl ly ạ̉nạ wyạk)2
 ạlqrạr- ṣlyby dạ kạn bdạlk .. wqbry dạ kạn mkạnk
 ạ̉nạ bdmy fdytk .. wbmwty qd ạ̉ḥyytk
 (tʿạl tʿạl tʿạl .. tʿạl ạ̹lyã ạlận)2
 2- (qạl ly yswʿ tʿạl .. blạsẖ tnẓr llḥạlẗ)2
 (ạ̉nạ fy lḥẓẗ ạ̉gẖyrk .. mạ ʿndy ḥạjẗ mḥạlẗ)2
 3- (ạ̉nạ bkẖṭạyạya ạ̉jy lk .. wtwbẗ qlby ạ̉dy lk)2
 (dạ ạ̹nt ạlly ḥbytny .. myn ygẖfr dẖnby gẖyrk)2
 4- (yạ yswʿ ạlḥbyb .. fạdyã wạ̉gẖly̱ nṣyb)2
 (ạ̉dy lk kl ḥyạty .. ʿnd qdmyk skyb)2</lyrics>
<title>qạl ly ạlsẖyṭạn</title>
</song>